Author: Fondo Platform
Title: [ANN][FDC - Token Sale] Fondo Trading Platform - The World's first SEICO.
Body: FONDO NETWORK THE WORLD'S FIRST SE-ICO The Platform for Crypto Exchange Website    Whitepaper    1. What is Fondo Network? Fondo Network is the world's first SE-ICO. It is a crypto UK-based blockchain ecosystem, consisting of a centralized trading platform, labs and launchpad for good ICO. Especially high security, low costs, high liquidity. Our trading exchange share 70% transaction fee for referrals and use 40% of all profits to burn coin.  2. What is Fondo Coin (FDC) - Token Issuance: 200,000,000 FDC. - Token sale: 100,000,000 FDC. Fondo Coin is the ERC20 Token of Fondo Network Exchange which is based on Ethereum ecosystem. Our trading exchange use 40% of all profits to buy back FDC and burn off every quarter.  https://i.imgur.com/LozAI5z.png  3. Referral Programs for Leader. ICO Referral program 10% of F1 downline sales (Pay by BTC/ETH)  Exchange Referral program: Up to 70% trading fee (Pay by BTC/ETH)  4. Token Sale Pre-sale end on July 23, 2018 Pre-sale price: $0.2 Total Pre-sale: 30,000,000 FDC Crowdsale from July 23, 2018 to August 22, 2018 Pre-sale price: $0.4 Total Pre-sale: 70,000,000 FDC - Accepted Currency: BTC, ETH.  5. The world's first SEICO SEICO - The new solution for investors who are suffering from losses or waiting for market to grow once again.  3 in 1 opportunity with only 1 investment.  - Profit from FDC price increases.  - Earn 85% profit from uneven amount when BTC and ETH increases. Initially, you invest 1 ETH at 500 USD per ETH to buy FDC, later on, ETH increase to 1,000 USD per ETH, then you will get 85% * 500 USD = 425 USD of difference in ETH.
